text: Brian Schrapel (born 17 May 1946) is an Australian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Australia Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
